1. Patient Management

-----------------------------------------------------------------------
UC-1.1: Register New Patient
Actor: Receptionist
Flow: Enter patient details (name, DOB, contact, address, blood group). 
System validates uniqueness by phone/email, generates patient ID, inserts record into patients table with auto-increment primary key.
------------------------------------------------------------------------

mysql> use jdbc_db;
		Database changed
		
mysql> create table patient
    -> (id int auto_increment primary key,
    -> name varchar(50),
    -> dob date,
    -> phone varchar(10) unique,
    -> email varchar(40) unique,
    -> address varchar(100),
    -> blood_group varchar(20));
Query OK, 0 rows affected (0.12 sec)

mysql> insert into patient(name, dob, phone, email, address, blood_group) values('tanisha pachpande', '2004-05-05', '964785', 'tanisha@gmail.com', 'a-56 bhopal', 'B+');
Query OK, 1 row affected (0.01 sec)

